										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>17 de las mejores propuestas de valor de e-commerce que hemos visto</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/es/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Value Propositions [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-115151" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-2.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fd086a56857e" class="block-preamble"><p>La competencia en el e-commerce es feroz. Y no hará más que intensificarse.</p>
</div>






<p>Con <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/439576/online-shopper-conversion-rate-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">2.42% de las visitas al e-commerce</a> convirtiéndose en compras, los marketeros están buscando constantemente nuevas formas de persuadir a los visitantes y destacarse de entre la multitud.</p>



<p>Con opciones infinitas de donde elegir, los consumidores se preguntan qué diferencia a tu marca de e-commerce.</p>



<p>La respuesta está escondida en tu <em>propuesta de valor.</em></p>



<p>Tu propuesta de valor es lo primero que quieres que tus clientes potenciales sepan sobre ti.</p>



<p>Con una propuesta de valor atractiva, puedes convencer a tus clientes potenciales a actuar y moverlos hacia abajo en tu <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">embudo de ventas del e-commerce</a>.</p>



<p>Pero, primero lo primero.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea163cd21ab2" class="block-content-upgrade">
