<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/bellroy-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Bellroy Marketing: Secretos de crecimiento de 7 millones de dólares de un innovador del comercio electrónico (Estudio de caso)</a></li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2">2. Construye poderosos Backlinks para tu tienda online</h2>



<p>A pesar de que la mayoría de las tiendas online dependen de la búsqueda en Google para su tráfico orgánico hoy en día, pocos vendedores de e-commerce conocen y aprecian la importancia del <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-seo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">SEO de e-commerce</a>.</p>



<p>Y aún menos gastan suficiente tiempo y esfuerzo en la construcción de enlaces.</p>



<p>Conseguir que páginas de alta autoridad se enlacen a tu tienda online hará que tu dominio sea más poderoso. Y un dominio poderoso te ayudará a superar a tus competidores en las páginas de resultados de los motores de búsqueda (SERP).</p>



<p>Seré sincero: la construcción de enlaces requiere tiempo y esfuerzo, pero los resultados valen la pena.</p>



<p>No importa si vendes ropa de hombre, muebles de diseño, libros para niños o regalos personalizados, lo más probable es que tu página de e-commerce (comercio electrónico) se especialice en algo.</p>



<p>Y hay una mayor posibilidad de que muchos editores ya estén escribiendo artículos sobre los mejores productos de tu industria.</p>



<p>Aquí entra en juego lo que Sam llama la estrategia «El mejor constructor de Backlinks».</p>



<p>En pocas palabras, llegas a los dominios de autoridad en tu industria y pides que te incluyan en su contenido «lo mejor de».</p>



<p>MeUndies es un gran ejemplo de esto. Puedes verlos en BuzzFeed bajo <a href="https://www.buzzfeed.com/kevinsmith/dope-shit-for-the-dope-guy-in-your-life" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">“21 regalos baratos para el chico guay de tu vida”</a> &#8230;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="875" height="382" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies.png" alt="4 BuzzFeed MeUndies" class="wp-image-112170" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies.png 875w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-768x335.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-600x262.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-760x332.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-740x323.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-BuzzFeed-MeUndies-385x168.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 875px) 100vw, 875px" /></figure></div>



<p>… as well as on smaller sites, like <a href="https://www.thepearlsource.com/blog/valentines-day-gifts-men-appreciate-love-use/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Pearl Source</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="631" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1024x631.png" alt="5 MeUndies Featured in The Pearl Source" class="wp-image-112174" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-1024x631.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-300x185.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-768x473.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-380x234.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-600x370.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-760x468.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-57x35.png 57w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-740x456.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-220x136.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source-385x237.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-MeUndies-Featured-in-The-Pearl-Source.png 1095w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Obtener backlinks de estos artículos » mejor de» ayuda a MeUndies a clasificar para varias palabras clave competitivas, como «calzoncillos boxer»:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="504" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-1024x504.png" alt="6 MeUndies SERP Results" class="wp-image-112178" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-1024x504.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-600x295.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-740x364.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-MeUndies-SERP-Results.png 1150w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>( Nota el número de backlinks que tienen).</p>



<p>MeUndies también patrocina varios podcasts, tanto para obtener enlaces de alta calidad como para ampliar su alcance a nuevas audiencias.</p>



<p>Por eso crean páginas de destino dedicadas para cada podcast que promocionan y ofrecen a sus oyentes un descuento especial:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="620" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-1024x620.png" alt="7 MeUndies Bill Burr Landing Page" class="wp-image-112182" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-1024x620.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-300x182.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-768x465.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-380x230.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-600x363.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-760x460.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-83x50.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-740x448.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-220x133.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page-385x233.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-MeUndies-Bill-Burr-Landing-Page.png 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>No sugiero llegar a los grandes nombres de tu industria y gastar todo tu presupuesto en patrocinios. Sin embargo, vale la pena probar esta estrategia con pequeños podcasts específicos para un determinado sector. También puedes construir fuertes vínculos y expandir tu alcance patrocinando eventos locales o premios.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Lectura adicional</strong></h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<ul><li><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing">9 Estrategias que los medios </a><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">utilizados</a><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/meundies-marketing"> para crecer 1,583% en 3 años (estudio de caso)</a></li></ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="3">3. Crear contenido para cada etapa de tu embudo</h2>



<p>Tanto si eres un principiante en tu campo como si eres un vendedor experimentado, es probable que sepas sobre la efectividad del contenido.</p>



<p>El mercadeo de contenido de e-commerce (comercio electrónico) puede ayudarte a adquirir nuevos posibles clientes y convertirlos en clientes.</p>



<p>Pero ningún contenido funcionará igual para diferentes personas.</p>



<p>Los usuarios en las diferentes etapas de su embudo de ventas tienen diferentes preguntas, preocupaciones y necesidades. Es por eso que necesita alinear su comercialización de contenido con el <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/the-buyers-journey" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">viaje del comprador</a>.</p>



<p>Esto no significa que tengas que escribir entradas de blog de 5.000 palabras para diferentes segmentos cada semana. Simplemente significa que necesitas encontrar las preguntas en la mente de tus posibles clientes y responderlas con tu contenido.</p>



<p>Tome Beardbrand como ejemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Los posibles clientes ToFu («parte superior del embudo») de la compañía probablemente tengan preguntas sobre cómo dejarse crecer la barba. Y cuando busquen ese término en Google, verán Beardbrand después de los fragmentos destacados:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="465" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-1024x465.png" alt="8 Beardbrand SERPs" class="wp-image-112186" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-1024x465.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-300x136.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-768x349.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-380x173.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-600x273.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-760x345.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-77x35.png 77w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-110x50.png 110w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-740x336.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-220x100.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs-385x175.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Beardbrand-SERPs.png 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>¿Por qué Beardbrand se clasifica tan bien para ese término? Bueno, más allá de tener un fuerte perfil de backlink, tienen una guía muy detallada sobre cómo dejarse crecer la barba:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="973" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-1024x973.png" alt="9 Beardbrand ToFu Content" class="wp-image-112190" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-1024x973.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-300x285.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-768x730.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-380x361.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-600x570.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-760x723.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-515x490.png 515w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-220x209.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content-385x366.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Beardbrand-ToFu-Content.png 1054w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Una vez que aprendes que debes cuidar mejor tu barba, poco a poco te interesas por los productos de Beardbrand.</p>



<p>Esto significa que te conviertes en un posible cliente de la compañía en la parte media del embudo (MoFu).</p>



<p>En esta etapa, Beardbrand tiene contenidos para educarte mientras promociona sutilmente sus productos. Así que si te preguntas cuál es la diferencia entre el aceite y el bálsamo para la barba, lo más probable es que termines en otro post de su blog:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="745" height="696" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content.png" alt="10 Beardbrand MoFu Content" class="wp-image-112194" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content.png 745w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-300x280.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-380x355.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-600x561.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-54x50.png 54w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-524x490.png 524w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-220x206.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Beardbrand-MoFu-Content-385x360.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y en esa entrada del blog, verás botones de <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">llamada a la acción</a> (CTA) para comprar sus productos:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="754" height="705" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA.png" alt="11 Beardbrand CTA" class="wp-image-112198" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA.png 754w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-300x281.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-380x355.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-600x561.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-37x35.png 37w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-53x50.png 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-524x490.png 524w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-220x206.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Beardbrand-CTA-385x360.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 754px) 100vw, 754px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si el blogging no forma parte de tu estrategia de marketing, intenta crear vídeos de «cómo hacer» para educar a tu público objetivo y promocionar sutilmente tus productos, tal y como hace Beardbrand:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="252" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--1024x252.png" alt="12 Beardbrand" class="wp-image-112202" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--1024x252.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--300x74.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--768x189.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--1536x378.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--380x94.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--600x148.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--760x187.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--1440x355.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--142x35.png 142w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--203x50.png 203w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--740x182.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--220x54.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand--385x95.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Beardbrand-.png 1990w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Visita Reddit o Quora para entender lo que tus posibles clientes están discutiendo, y luego crea contenido para responder a sus preguntas. Implementar la comercialización de productos en tu estrategia de contenido, sin ser un vendedor obvio.</p>



