<h2 id="4">4. Recuperar carritos abandonados con un giro</h2>



<p>El abandono del carrito es la pesadilla de todo comerciante de e-commerce (comercio electrónico).</p>



<p>Según <a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Baymard</a>, el promedio de abandono de carros en el e-commerce (comercio electrónico) es cercano al 70%. Esto significa que la mayoría de sus visitantes dejarán su sitio sin comprar los artículos de su carrito.</p>



<p>Mientras que el abandono del carrito es inevitable, afortunadamente hay algo que puedes hacer para minimizarlo.</p>



<p>Con una <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/checkout-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">facturación optimizada</a> y <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/abandoned-cart-emails" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">emails bien escritos sobre carritos abandonados</a>, puedes ir más allá de recuperar los carritos abandonados e incluso vender más.</p>



<p>Al final, no sólo recuperarás los posibles ingresos perdidos, sino que también aumentarás el <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/average-order-value" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">valor medio de los pedidos</a> (AOV).</p>



<p>Harry&#8217;s tiene una estrategia genial para recuperar los carritos abandonados (con un giro.)</p>



<p>Cuando abandonas el sitio de Harry&#8217;s sin haber iniciado tu suscripción, recibes un email que te recuerda que debes completar el proceso.</p>



<p>En principio, se parece a cualquier otro email de carrito abandonado:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="575" height="809" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png" alt="13 Harry_s Abandoned Cart Email" class="wp-image-112206" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email.png 575w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-213x300.png 213w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-380x535.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-25x35.png 25w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-36x50.png 36w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-348x490.png 348w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-220x310.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Harry_s-Abandoned-Cart-Email-385x542.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px" /></figure>



<p>In the first part of the email, Harry’s reminds you about the benefit of buying a subscription plan.</p>



<p>But in the second part, things get interesting.</p>



<p>Harry’s offers you a <em>downsell, </em>in case you’re not ready to commit to a subscription.&nbsp;</p>



<p>But they don’t stop there.</p>



<p>When you follow the link and add the Truman Set to your cart, this time they <em>upsell </em>with a popup suggesting a mystery item.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="477" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png" alt="14 Harry_s Upsell Popup" class="wp-image-112210" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-1024x477.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Harry_s-Upsell-Popup.png 1387w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>De esta manera, te llevan de vuelta a un precio más alto, incluso si no estás listo para comprometerte con un plan de suscripción.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3>Nota del editor&nbsp;</h3>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Si quieres aumentar las ventas de un cliente con un artículo misterioso exclusivo (o <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/upselling" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cualquier otro artículo</a>), puedes crear una campaña con nuestra nueva condición de <a href="https://sleeknote.com/features/sitedata" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Datos de la web</a> y mostrar la ventana emergente a los visitantes que superen un determinado valor de la cesta.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="707" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData.png" alt="15 Sleeknote-SiteData" class="wp-image-112214" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData.png 707w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Sleeknote-SiteData-385x224.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 707px) 100vw, 707px" /></figure>
