<h2 id="5">5. Aprovecha al máximo tus comentarios de los clientes</h2>



<p>Cuando se trata de <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">testimonios de clientes</a>, hay dos desafíos principales que esperan a los vendedores de e-commerce (comercio electrónico):</p>



<ul><li>Recopilar la mayor cantidad de revisiones ricas y perspicaces como sea posible; y</li><li>Usando esas críticas de la mejor manera posible para convencer a tus posibles clientes de que te compren.</li><li>La forma en que pidas testimonios puede tener un gran impacto tanto en la cantidad como en la calidad de las reseñas que recojas.</li></ul>



<p>Incluso si convences a tus clientes de que dejen una reseña de un producto, la mayoría de las veces son demasiado genéricas y amplias.</p>



<p>Casper encuentra una solución inteligente a este problema común. Unos días después de convertirte en cliente, la compañía te envía este email pidiendo una reseña del producto:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png" alt="16 Casper_s Review Email" class="wp-image-112218" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-300x251.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-768x643.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-380x318.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-600x503.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-760x637.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-585x490.png 585w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-220x184.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email-385x322.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Review-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Al hacer clic en el botón CTA, aterrizas en una página donde puedes enviar el siguiente formulario y dejar una reseña:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="743" height="672" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form.png" alt="17 Casper Review Form" class="wp-image-112222" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form.png 743w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-300x271.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-380x344.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-600x543.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-55x50.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-542x490.png 542w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-220x199.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Casper-Review-Form-385x348.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper te invita a responder algunas preguntas específicas en lugar de dejarlo completamente abierto. De esta manera, se hace más fácil para sus clientes llenar el formulario.</p>



<p>Además, se enriquecen y se hacen más significativas las reseñas de productos, como esta:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="963" height="218" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example.png" alt="18 Casper Review Example" class="wp-image-112226" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example.png 963w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-768x174.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-600x136.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-760x172.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-960x218.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-155x35.png 155w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-221x50.png 221w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-740x168.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-Casper-Review-Example-385x87.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 963px) 100vw, 963px" /></figure></div>



<p>La forma de mostrar tus críticas es tan importante como coleccionarlas.</p>



<p>Puedes reutilizar los testimonios de tus clientes a través de varios canales: Úsalos en tus emails, páginas de productos, anuncios pagados y muchos más.</p>



<p>Inspírate en Casper otra vez. Ambos muestran las opiniones de los clientes en una página dedicada&#8230;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="411" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-1024x411.png" alt="19 Casper Reviews Page" class="wp-image-112230" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-1024x411.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-300x120.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-768x308.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-380x152.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-600x241.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-760x305.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-87x35.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-125x50.png 125w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-740x297.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-220x88.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page-385x154.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper-Reviews-Page.png 1413w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230; y lo utilizan en su marketing por email como prueba social:</p>



