<h2 id="6">6. Create an Irresistible Unboxing Experience</h2>



<p>Con el aumento de los contenidos generados por los usuarios y el boca a boca electrónico, el fenómeno del «desembalaje,»&nbsp; entró rápidamente en nuestras vidas.</p>



<p>No es una coincidencia que hoy en día<a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/unboxtherapy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"> un canal de YouTube sobre «desembalaje»</a> (Unboxing) tenga más de 14 millones de suscriptores.</p>



<p>Tanto a los consumidores como a los vendedores les encantan los videos de «desembalaje,». Porque ayudan a los consumidores a obtener una visión detallada de los productos que les interesan. Y significan una prueba social y más alcance para los vendedores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para crear una experiencia de «desembalaje» irresistible para sus clientes, es necesario establecer sus expectativas desde el principio.</p>



<p>Man Crates lo hace bien burlándose de la experiencia de «desembalaje,». Cuando ingresas tu código postal en una de sus <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/product-page-optimization" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">páginas de productos</a>, la compañía te da una fecha estimada de entrega:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-1024x497.png" alt="21 Man Crates Estimate Delivery Date.png" class="wp-image-112238" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Man-Crates-Estimate-Delivery-Date.png 1204w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Además, te dan más información sobre cómo se enviará tu entrega:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="596" height="355" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships.png" alt="22 Man Crates How It Ships" class="wp-image-112242" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships.png 596w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-300x179.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-380x226.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-59x35.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-84x50.png 84w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-220x131.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Man-Crates-How-It-Ships-385x229.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 596px) 100vw, 596px" /></figure></div>



<p>Durante el proceso de compra, también te permiten escribir una nota de regalo y mejorar la experiencia de desembalar del destinatario del regalo.</p>



<p>Y aún mejor, sugieren algunas divertidas notas pre-escritas para elegir:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="238" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-1024x238.png" alt="23 Man Crates Gift Note" class="wp-image-112246" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-1024x238.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-300x70.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-768x178.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-380x88.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-600x139.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-760x176.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-151x35.png 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-216x50.png 216w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-740x172.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-220x51.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note-385x89.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Man-Crates-Gift-Note.png 1388w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



